headline: Cardinal Health (NYSE:CAH) Launches One Voice Initiative Supporting Independent Pharmacy Advocacy
summary: Cardinal Health (NYSE:CAH) recently launched its Cardinal Health™ One Voice Initiative, a move aimed at advocating for independent pharmacies, which aligns with the company's broader strategic efforts in product development and community support. Over the last quarter, the company's stock price rose by 22%, reflecting not only this initiative but also the increased dividend payout, which may have appealed to income-focused investors.
